@startuml 01-context-stack
title dteam / unios / unibit / nightly Rust — Context Stack

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Human operator /\nexecutive / analyst" as Human
actor "Auditor /\nreceipt verifier" as Auditor
actor "Internal builder" as Builder

rectangle "dteam\nDeterministic process intelligence.\nConsumes canonical facts.\nEmits verified results + receipts." as DTEAM
rectangle "unios\nPrivate admission / proof / projection\noperating contract layer." as UNIOS
rectangle "unibit\nSealed substrate.\nResident truth + scratch,\nbranchless lawful motion." as UNIBIT
rectangle "Nightly Rust\nPrivate compiler surface:\nconst generics, asm, SIMD,\npinned layout, provenance lints." as NIGHTLY

Human --> DTEAM : submits process challenges\nviews verified results
Auditor --> DTEAM : verifies receipts
Auditor ..> UNIOS : does not see
Auditor ..> UNIBIT : does not see
Builder --> UNIBIT : builds sealed substrate
Builder --> UNIOS : builds operating layer

DTEAM --> UNIOS : calls only public operating contract
UNIOS --> UNIBIT : submits admitted typed handles
UNIBIT --> NIGHTLY : implemented with

DTEAM ..> UNIBIT : does not know
DTEAM ..> NIGHTLY : does not know
UNIOS ..> NIGHTLY : does not know internals

@enduml
